 Task 2 — Vehicle Engine Selection System
 Objective:
Demonstrate @Qualifier to inject a specific engine type (Diesel / Electric / Petrol) into a Vehicle
class.
 Class-wise Design
1. Interface — Engine
Method:
void start();
2 .Implementations:
DieselEngine: prints "Diesel engine started "
ElectricEngine: prints "Electric engine started "
PetrolEngine: prints "Petrol engine started "
3 . Class — Vehicle
Field:
Engine engine
Injection:
@Autowired
@Qualifier("electricEngine")
Method:
startVehicle() → call engine.start()
4 . AppConfig Class
@Configuration, @ComponentScan("com.example")
5 .MainApp Class
Load context
Get Vehicle bean
Call startVehicle()
 Expected Output:
Electric engine started